com.cognifide.slice.core.internal.injector

Class InjectorWithContextImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cognifide.slice.core.internal.injector.InjectorWithContextImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InjectorWithContext, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class InjectorWithContextImpl
extends Object
implements InjectorWithContext
    Author:
    Rafa≈Ç Malinowski Decoration for Guice Injector class with simple access to modyfing and restoring ContextProvider. For use in Servlets or Services use following idiom: 
     
 final InjectorWithContext injector = InjectorsRepository.getInjector(APP_NAME);
 final SimpleContextProvider simpleContextProvider = new SimpleContextProvider();
 simpleContextProvider.setContext(ContextFactory.getServletRequestContext(request, response));
 
 injector.pushContextProvider(simpleContextProvider);
 try {
   ...
 } finally {
   injector.popContextProvider();
 }
    to ensure that injector is left in a state that is was before. This decoration has two delegate getInstance() methods added for convenience.
